text: Amorn Yuktanandana (born 16 June 1928, date of death unknown) was a Thai sports shooter. He competed at the 1960, 1964, 1968 Summer Olympics and 1958 and 1966 Asian Games. ==References== Category:1928 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Thai male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Thailand Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Asian Games medalists in shooting Category:Shooters at the 1958 Asian Games Category:Shooters at the 1966 Asian Games Category:Asian Games silver medalists for Thailand Category:Medalists at the 1958 Asian Games Category:Medalists at the 1966 Asian Games
